hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吊住你, 但又唔比你死晒, 慢慢咁燒晒D 錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T02:16:27.000Z","msg":"唔識唔好亂講<br />\n中興失去意大利訂單，有分析指這有助中興更積極參與阿非拉國家建設，中國或成為最大贏家。"},{"pid":"e4ecc38e9606cc7a4d732277d80074d835a39d24","tid":729700,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08af9fdc1dc325693e47a05ddee2f7d11b06c53f","tid":729700,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T02:08:36.000Z","msg":"原來比中興番生係做維修"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"好絕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a0fe1e0badaba9991a6fc06aeddc48b148f0b4","tid":729700,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f37efb486c937481b7e16ca87a0c5cc670e3da","tid":729700,"uid":190431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5bfa1856465fbc2aa15a260941b1396ebfd5e0c6","tid":729700,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T02:11:28.000Z","msg":"好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中興比美國慢性玩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吊住你, 但又唔比你死晒, 慢慢咁燒晒D 錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T02:16:27.000Z","msg":"唔識唔好亂講<br />\n中興失去意大利訂單，有分析指這有助中興更積極參與阿非拉國家建設，中國或成為最大贏家。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"贏到好攰"}]}